t":"余给她读了点绘本就熟起来啦","from":327.452,"location":2,"to":330.371},{"content":"虽然是个什么王子殿下跟公主殿下","from":330.621,"location":2,"to":332.749},{"content":"那种骗小孩的故事就是了","from":332.749,"location":2,"to":335.376},{"content":"后续的故事就下次再念吧","from":335.376,"location":2,"to":337.17},{"content":"抱歉","from":337.879,"location":2,"to":338.671},{"content":"你妹妹吗","from":338.963,"location":2,"to":340.84},{"content":"怎么可能","from":340.84,"location":2,"to":341.758},{"content":"辛耶","from":341.758,"location":2,"to":342.717},{"content":"汝多的是时间吧","from":343.76,"location":2,"to":346.679},{"content":"陪余来一下","from":346.679,"location":2,"to":348.264},{"content":"虽然还有点早","from":362.862,"location":2,"to":364.405},{"content":"但要不要参考看看圣诞礼品呢","from":364.405,"location":2,"to":366.991},{"content":"还会赠送精美小礼哦","from":366.991,"location":2,"to":368.201},{"content":"您妹妹这么可爱嘛","from":368.201,"location":2,"to":369.786},{"content":"怎么可能","from":370.244,"location":2,"to":371.371},{"content":"葛格","from":371.371,"location":2,"to":372.914},{"content":"人家好想要哦","from":373.873,"location":2,"to":377.46},{"content":"人家…","from":379.504,"location":2,"to":381.881},{"content":"想要…","from":381.881,"location":2,"to":383.925},{"content":"没想到汝这么好骗啊","from":390.056,"location":2,"to":392.35},{"content":"你是在哪里学到那种东西的","from":392.35,"location":2,"to":395.061},{"content":"明天我要早点回家","from":433.641,"location":2,"to":435.518},{"content":"所以今天会再留晚一点","from":435.518,"location":2,"to":437.437},{"content":"毕竟明天是圣诞前夜祭嘛","from":437.437,"location":2,"to":439.605},{"content":"共和国那边似乎也有送礼物的习俗","from":440.022,"location":2,"to":443.901},{"content":"礼物是吧","from":444.444,"location":2,"to":445.778},{"content":"该送什么才好呢","from":446.404,"location":2,"to":448.072},{"content":"他们来到这里也有一个月了","from":449.615,"location":2,"to":452.326},{"content":"各自都有交到朋友  也找到事情做","from":453.077,"location":2,"to":455.455},{"content":"看上去还满融入的样子","from":455.788,"location":2,"to":457.665},{"content":"这样啊","from":458.124,"location":2,"to":458.708},{"content":"交到朋友算是好征兆呢","from":459.167,"location":2,"to":461.836},{"content":"这样应该没问题了吧","from":462.378,"location":2,"to":464.297},{"content":"到了春天","from":465.006,"location":2,"to":465.715},{"content":"无论他们的出路或是什么事情","from":465.715,"location":2,"to":467.133},{"content":"我都得先准备准备才行","from":467.133,"location":2,"to":469.427},{"content":"我知道这是很过分的要求","from":483.107,"location":2,"to":485.651},{"content":"你们已经抵达终点了","from":487.153,"location":2,"to":489.947},{"content":"也遵守约定把我们带到那里","from":490.656,"location":2,"to":493.284},{"content":"所以  其实把我们忘了也没关系","from":493.868,"location":2,"to":498.498},{"content":"但明知如此…","from":499.457,"location":2,"to":502.126},{"content":"我还是觉得好痛苦","from":503.044,"location":2,"to":504.962},{"content":"继续留在世上真的好煎熬","from":506.172,"location":2,"to":508.591},{"content":"我们已经死了  所以只想回去而已","from":509.675,"location":2,"to":511.844},{"content":"因此","from":513.262,"location":2,"to":514.18},{"content":"辛","from":514.514,"location":2,"to":515.306},{"content":"我们的死神啊","from":515.973,"location":2,"to":517.517},{"content":"能不能请你救救我们呢","from":522.188,"location":2,"to":525.316},{"content":"辛","from":533.032,"location":2,"to":534.116},{"content":"就算太阳出来了很温暖","from":537.578,"location":2,"to":539.622},{"content":"（星历2148年 12月24日）","from":539.622,"location":2,"to":539.914},{"content":"在这里睡觉还是会被图书馆员骂哦\n（星历2148年 12月24日）","from":539.914,"location":2,"to":542.166},{"content":"你昨天熬夜了吗\n（星历2148年 12月24日）","from":542.166,"location":2,"to":543.584},{"content":"那倒是没有","from":544.126,"location":2,"to":545.92},{"content":"时间也差不多了  要不要去看看","from":547.255,"location":2,"to":549.632},{"content":"要看什么","from":550.091,"location":2,"to":550.925},{"content":"圣诞前夜祭的军队游行啊","from":550.925,"location":2,"to":553.511},{"content":"今年出场的是西方方面军第二四机甲师团","from":554.011,"location":2,"to":557.848},{"content":"所以应该可以看到最新型的第三期改版破坏之杖哦","from":557.848,"location":2,"to":561.769},{"content":"你该不会没兴趣吧","from":563.688,"location":2,"to":565.273},{"content":"不是…","from":565.565,"location":2,"to":566.315},{"content":"但你看上去才不像是会对这种事感兴趣的人","from":566.315,"location":2,"to":569.485},{"content":"因为我啊  决定从军了","from":570.82,"location":2,"to":572.363},{"content":"我希望能加入机甲科","from":573.155,"location":2,"to":574.865},{"content":"所以才想去看看当作学习的一环","from":575.199,"location":2,"to":577.535},{"content":"就这方面来说  我以为你也是同类人","from":578.035,"location":2,"to":581.163},{"content":"不只是昨天","from":582.039,"location":2,"to":583.165},{"content":"之前我也看你在翻阅军事相关的资料","from":583.165,"location":2,"to":585.71},{"content":"才会以为你或许也是想报考特军校","from":585.71,"location":2,"to":588.963},{"content":"这里虽然一派和平","from":590.673,"location":2,"to":592.425},{"content":"但国境线上还是在打仗","from":592.425,"location":2,"to":594.302},{"content":"而且也不知道战火何时会蔓延过来","from":594.594,"location":2,"to":597.43},{"content":"为了不让这种事发生","from":598.097,"location":2,"to":599.473},{"content":"我才会想尽量去做可以保护妹妹以及这座城市的事","from":599.89,"location":2,"to":603.936},{"content":"总有一天  我想带妹妹去看看大海","from":604.687,"location":2,"to":608.274},{"content":"所以非得终结这场战争才行","from":608.941,"location":2,"to":612.32},{"content":"说的也是","from":613.571,"location":2,"to":614.655},{"content":"那我先过去了","from":616.699,"location":2,"to":618.075},{"content":"你有兴趣的话就过来吧","from":618.326,"location":2,"to":619.827},{"content":"休息太久了啊","from":627.293,"location":2,"to":628.919},{"content":"（那种事 事到如今）","from":634.091,"location":2,"to":637.011},{"content":"（星历2148年 12月24日）","from":637.011,"location":2,"to":639.263},{"content":"终于找到你了","from":656.489,"location":2,"to":657.74},{"content":"你说今天要去共和广场附近","from":658.199,"location":2,"to":661.41},{"content":"我就来碰碰运气了","from":661.41,"location":2,"to":663.329},{"content":"怎么了","from":664.33,"location":2,"to":665.122},{"content":"我想找你帮个忙","from":665.414,"location":2,"to":667.208},{"content":"主要是搬东西  只有我实在拿不动","from":667.208,"location":2,"to":670.419},{"content":"好哦","from":670.753,"location":2,"to":671.629},{"content":"还要找谁来吗","from":671.921,"location":2,"to":673.422},{"content":"辛大概有空吧","from":673.422,"location":2,"to":675.049},{"content":"辛…","from":675.049,"location":2,"t